1. *Hitnu* pomoć treba odmah pozvati. (Emergency help needs to be called immediately.)
2. On je tražio *hitnu* intervenciju. (He asked for an urgent intervention.)
3. Ona je poslala *hitnu* poruku. (She sent an urgent message.)
4. Treba da pošaljete *hitnu* obaveštenje. (You should send an urgent notification.)
5. Njegov *hitan* odgovor je bio da. (His urgent response was yes.)
6. Ona je zatražila *hitnu* pomoć. (She asked for immediate assistance.)
7. On je potrebno da učini *hitnu* akciju. (He needs to take immediate action.)